title: Patricia Locke Cassie Earrings—Bermuda
description:
The Cassie earring represents a small, sassy, fun part of the constellation, Cassiopeia, named after the famed beauty queen of Greek mythology. Patricia Locke jewelry speaks a distinctive visual language that encourages self-expression, with an aura of romance and femininity.

  • Dimensions: .25 x .75 in.
  • Materials: antique silver and gold plated pewter set with Swarovski crystals in Bermuda
